---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Landing Page Informativa | Digital Solutions">
  
  <!-- 1. HERO SECTION -->
  <section class="relative bg-[#1d4ed8] text-white pt-32 pb-16 lg:pt-48 lg:pb-32 overflow-hidden flex items-center">
    <!-- Abstract Shapes -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-2/3 h-full bg-[#2563eb] rounded-bl-full opacity-50 pointer-events-none transform translate-x-1/4"></div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 w-full fade-in-up text-center lg:text-left">
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-16">
        <div class="w-full lg:w-3/5 space-y-8">
          <div class="inline-block bg-[#3b82f6] text-white px-5 py-2 rounded-full text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] shadow-sm">
            Conversión de Alto Impacto
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-[7.5rem] font-black tracking-tighter leading-[0.9] lg:leading-[0.8] mb-6">
            Landing Page<br />
            <span class="text-[#60a5fa]">Informativa<span class="text-white">.</span></span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg lg:text-xl text-blue-100 max-w-xl leading-relaxed font-medium mx-auto lg:mx-0">
            Arquitectura de conversión acelerada. Ingeniería de una sola página optimizada para capturar leads y maximizar el ROI de tus campañas.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 pt-4 justify-center lg:justify-start">
             <a href="https://wa.me/584124683230" class="bg-white text-[#1d4ed8] px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm hover:bg-blue-50 transition-all shadow-xl">Iniciar Proyecto</a>
             <a href="/precios" class="bg-white/10 border border-white/20 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm hover:bg-white/20 transition-all">Ver Otros Planes</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="w-full lg:w-2/5 relative hidden lg:block">
           <div class="aspect-square bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0ea5e9] to-[#2563eb] rounded-[3.5rem] rotate-3 relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border border-white/10 group flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-600/10 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700"></div>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center opacity-20 group-hover:rotate-12 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-700">
                 <svg class="w-48 h-48 text-white relative z-10" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"><path d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
              </div>
           </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 2. ANATOMÍA DE CONVERSIÓN -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-[#f8fafc] border-b border-slate-100">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      
      <div class="mb-20 text-center md:text-left">
          <span class="text-[#2563eb] font-black text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase block mb-4">Ingeniería UX</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-[#0f172a] tracking-tighter leading-none mb-6">
            Anatomía de <span class="text-[#2563eb]">Conversión.</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-slate-500 font-medium text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto md:mx-0">
            Cada sección, botón y párrafo están estratégicamente ubicados para minimizar la fricción cognitiva y acelerar la toma de decisiones del lead potencial.
          </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        
        <!-- Block 1 -->
        <div class="eng-hover p-10 border border-slate-100 bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-xl transition-all h-full">
          <div class="mb-10 text-slate-400 font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-[#2563eb]">Paso 01</span>
            <span class="bg-blue-50 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px]">Estructura</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#eff6ff] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#2563eb]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-[#0f172a] mb-4 tracking-tight leading-none">Diseño<br/>Sin Fugas.</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed font-medium">Eliminamos distracciones y menús de navegación complejos. El lead entra a la página para convertirse en potencial cliente.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Block 2 (Copywriting) -->
        <div class="eng-hover col-span-1 md:col-span-2 bg-[#1e40af] rounded-[2.5rem] p-10 md:p-14 flex flex-col justify-between text-white hover:shadow-2xl transition-all overflow-hidden relative group">
          <div class="absolute -right-20 -top-20 text-[20rem] font-black opacity-[0.05] leading-none pointer-events-none select-none group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-1000">" "</div>
          <div class="mb-10 text-[#93c5fd] font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest relative z-10 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-8 h-px bg-[#93c5fd]/50"></span> 02 / PERSUASIÓN
          </div>
          <div class="relative z-10 w-full md:w-3/4">
            <h3 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-8 tracking-tighter leading-none">Copywriting Corporativo.</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-100 text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium">
               Textos estructurados bajo frameworks de marketing efectivos que conectan los dolores de tu cliente con la urgencia y el valor de los beneficios exclusivos de tu negocio.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Block 3 -->
        <div class="eng-hover col-span-1 md:col-span-2 p-10 md:p-14 border border-slate-100 bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-xl transition-all h-full">
          <div class="mb-10 text-[#2563eb] font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] relative flex items-center gap-2">
             <span class="w-8 h-px bg-[#2563eb]/30"></span> 03 / CAPTACIÓN
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-12 items-center">
            <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
               <h3 class="text-4xl font-black text-[#0f172a] mb-6 tracking-tighter leading-none">Formularios Optimizados.</h3>
               <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed text-sm font-medium">
                 El destino final del Funnel. Diseñamos módulos interactivos de prospección que reducen drásticamente la fricción, enviando el prospecto directo a tu email o CRM.
               </p>
            </div>
            <!-- Mock UI Panel -->
            <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col gap-4 bg-slate-50 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 shadow-inner">
               <div class="w-full h-12 bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 px-5 flex items-center text-xs font-bold text-slate-400">Nombre Corporativo</div>
               <div class="w-full h-12 bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 px-5 flex items-center text-xs font-bold text-slate-400">Email Profesional</div>
               <div class="w-full h-12 bg-[#2563eb] rounded-xl shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(37,99,235,0.3)] flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest transition-all hover:scale-[1.02]">
                 Solicitar Llamada
               </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Block 4 -->
        <div class="eng-hover p-10 bg-[#2563eb] rounded-[2.5rem] flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-2xl transition-all text-white group overflow-hidden relative">
          <div class="absolute -right-10 -bottom-10 opacity-10 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-700">
             <svg class="w-40 h-40" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 18h.01M8 21h8a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-10 text-white/50 font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest relative z-10">
            04 / EXPERIENCIA
          </div>
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <h3 class="text-4xl font-black mb-6 tracking-tighter leading-none">Mobile<br/>First.</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-100 text-sm font-medium leading-relaxed">
              El 80% del tráfico ocurre en móviles. Integramos una UX insuperable para smartphones.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 3. ARCHITECTURE & PRICING -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-white relative">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-20 items-center">
        
        <!-- Left: Technical Specs -->
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
           <span class="text-[#2563eb] font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase block mb-4">Ingeniería Técnica</span>
           <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-[#0f172a] tracking-tighter leading-none mb-10">Despliegue de<br/> <span class="text-[#2563eb]">Grado Superior.</span></h2>
           
           <div class="space-y-8">
              <div class="eng-hover flex gap-6 items-start p-8 rounded-[2rem] bg-slate-50/50 border border-transparent hover:bg-white transition-all shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl">
                 <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-white flex items-center justify-center text-[#2563eb] border border-slate-100 shadow-sm shrink-0">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
                 </div>
                 <div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-[#0f172a] text-xl mb-2">Carga Extrema < 0.5s</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium leading-relaxed">Arquitectura estática (Astro Islands) para dar una respuesta inmediata, evitando que tus clientes cierren la web antes de cargar.</p>
                 </div>
              </div>
              <div class="eng-hover flex gap-6 items-start p-8 rounded-[2rem] bg-slate-50/50 border border-transparent hover:bg-white transition-all shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl">
                 <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-white flex items-center justify-center text-[#2563eb] border border-slate-100 shadow-sm shrink-0">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M17 8h2a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2v4l-4-4H9a1.994 1.994 0 01-1.414-.586m0 0L11 14h4a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2v4l.586-.586z"></path></svg>
                 </div>
                 <div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-[#0f172a] text-xl mb-2">WhatsApp Direct API</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium leading-relaxed">Integración con enlaces y mensajes preconfigurados, llevando al lead directamente al embudo de citas de WhatsApp.</p>
                 </div>
              </div>
              <div class="eng-hover flex gap-6 items-start p-8 rounded-[2rem] bg-slate-50/50 border border-transparent hover:bg-white transition-all shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl">
                 <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-white flex items-center justify-center text-[#2563eb] border border-slate-100 shadow-sm shrink-0">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path></svg>
                 </div>
                 <div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-[#0f172a] text-xl mb-2">Certificado SSL & Dominio</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium leading-relaxed">Cifrado de grado bancario (HTTPS). La insignia de candado en tu web consolida la confianza de la transacción digital.</p>
                 </div>
              </div>
           </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Pricing Card -->
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex justify-center">
           <div class="eng-hover glow-on-hover relative bg-white rounded-[4rem] p-12 lg:p-16 border border-slate-100 shadow-[0_20px_60px_rgba(37,99,235,0.05)] overflow-hidden group hover:border-[#2563eb] transition-all duration-700 w-full max-w-xl">
              <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-10 opacity-[0.03] pointer-events-none group-hover:opacity-[0.08] transition-opacity">
                 <svg class="w-40 h-40 text-[#2563eb]" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-10 text-center relative z-10">
                 <span class="text-slate-300 text-sm font-black line-through mb-1 uppercase tracking-widest opacity-70 block">$300 USD</span>
                 <div class="flex items-baseline justify-center gap-3">
                    <span class="text-8xl font-black text-[#2563eb] tracking-tighter leading-none">$180</span>
                    <span class="text-slate-400 text-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] relative -top-3">Total</span>
                 </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-6 text-left mb-12 w-full max-w-lg mx-auto border-y border-slate-100 py-8 relative z-10">
                 <li class="flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-600 font-bold text-[12px] list-none"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#2563eb] shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Diseño Fast-Track</li>
                 <li class="flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-600 font-bold text-[12px] list-none"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#2563eb] shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Copywriting Persuasivo</li>
                 <li class="flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-600 font-bold text-[12px] list-none"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#2563eb] shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Formulario de Contacto</li>
                 <li class="flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-600 font-bold text-[12px] list-none"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#2563eb] shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Botón de WhatsApp API</li>
                 <li class="flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-600 font-bold text-[12px] list-none"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#2563eb] shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Mobile-First Extremo</li>
                 <li class="flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-600 font-bold text-[12px] list-none"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#2563eb] shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Hosting Incluido 1 Año</li>
              </div>

              <a href="https://wa.me/584124683230" target="_blank" class="w-full py-6 bg-[#25D366] hover:bg-[#22c55e] text-white font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] rounded-[2rem] shadow-[0_15px_40px_rgba(34,197,94,0.3)] transition-all hover:scale-[1.02] flex items-center justify-center gap-3 relative z-10 text-sm">
                 Activar Proyecto
                 <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"></path></svg>
              </a>
           </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
